The next National Conference is  March 11-14, 2003 in Albuquerque, NM.

The 5th (!!) Annual NIH SBIR/STTR Conference will be held June 2-3, 2003 in
Bethesda, MD



Frequent our website and http://www.sbirworld.com
<http://www.sbirworld.com/>  or http://www.zyn.com/sbir
